msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Current built-in revision level of the default Madnox values to reset / initialize the skin."
msgstr "Núverandi innbygda útgávustøði hjá standard Madnox-virðunum til at endurstovna/ræsa skinið."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31507"
msgid "Select if an intro video will play when Kodi is first started. None: No video, Built-In: Kodi's release level intro video, Custom: Pick video of your choice to display."
msgstr "Vel um eitt intro-video skal spæla, tá ið Kodi verður ræst. Ongantíð: Einki video, Innbygt: Útgávuvideo hjá Kodi, Sérgjørt: Vel egið video at vísa."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31508"
msgid "This setting forces the media flag to resolution flag as 4K or 2160p providing user icon control without skin modifcations."
msgstr "Henda stilling tvingar miðlamerkið til upploysnismerki sum 4K ella 2160p, og gevur brúkranum íkonstýring uttan skin-broytingar."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31509"
msgid "Change the stars color displayed in the video info line. Click to cycle through fixed colors or select a custom color."
msgstr "Broyt litin á stjørnunum, ið verða vístir í videokunningarlinjuni. Trýst fyri at skifta millum fastsettar litir ella vel ein sérgjørdan lit."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31510"
msgid "Allows star ratings style to use a custom color when it is set to \"Custom\"."
msgstr "Loyvir stjørnustílinum at nýta ein sérgjørdan lit, tá ið hesin er settur til \"Sérgjørt\"."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Dedicated addon for Madnox required for Piers+. Moves all free running scripts to a dedicated addon for security purposes."
msgstr "Serstakt ískoyti til Madnox, ið krevst til Piers+. Flytur øll fríttkeyrandi skript yvir í eitt serstakt ískoyti av trygdarávum."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "TMDbHelper provides several tools to assist skinners with retrieving information from TMDb, OMDb and Trakt APIs."
msgstr "TMDbHelper veitir fleiri tól til at hjálpa skin-evnarum við at heinta upplýsingar frá TMDb, OMDb og Trakt API."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31513"
msgid "Wikipedia addon for Kodi."
msgstr "Wikipedia-ískoyti til Kodi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31514"
msgid "Advanced CinemaVision replacement that can be enabled to replace Madnox's built in simpler CinemaMode. Allows the ultimate CinemaMode experience and customisation."
msgstr "Fjøltáttað CinemaVision-avloysing, sum kann verða virkt fyri at loysa ta innbygdu einfaldu CinemaMode-støðuna hjá Madnox av. Tryggjar ta bestu biografstøðuupplivingina og sérgerðarmøguleikarnar."

