msgstr "Vís metingar sum 10-stiga tøl"

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31524"
msgid "Allows changes to the ratings to convert between floating numbers or as a percentage. Affects TMDb & IMDb, all others remain as their default display."
msgstr "Loyvir broytingum í metingum at konvertera millum desimaltøl ella sum prosentpart. Ávirkar TMDb & IMDb, allar aðrar verða standandi við teirra standardvísing."

